Interface ParticipantVideo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Observable, ParticipantService

    public interface ParticipantVideo
extends ParticipantService
    This interface represents the video capabilities of a participant in the conversation.

    • Field Detail

      • PARTICIPANT_VIDEO_PAUSED_PROPERTY_ID

        static final int PARTICIPANT_VIDEO_PAUSED_PROPERTY_ID
        Property ID for notifying that paused state of the participant video has changed. Subscribers will be notified via the onPropertyChanged method on the Observable.OnPropertyChangedCallback interface with this property id. E.g. callback.onPropertyChanged(PARTICIPANT_VIDEO_PAUSED_PROPERTY_ID). Clients are expected to call the isPaused method in the callback to get the changed state.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PARTICIPANT_VIDEO_CANSUBSCRIBE_PROPERTY_ID

        static final int PARTICIPANT_VIDEO_CANSUBSCRIBE_PROPERTY_ID
        Property ID for notifying that clients can subscribe to the participants video. Subscribers will be notified via the onPropertyChanged method on the Observable.OnPropertyChangedCallback interface with this property id. E.g. callback.onPropertyChanged(PARTICIPANT_VIDEO_CANSUBSCRIBE_PROPERTY_ID). Clients are expected to call the canSubscribe method in the callback to check if the participants video can be subscribed to.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

    • Method Detail

      • isPaused

        boolean isPaused()
        Returns if the participant's video is paused or is being sent into the conversation. Video from the local endpoint can be paused via the VideoService
        Returns:
        boolean true if paused, false otherwise.

      • subscribe

        void subscribe(MMVRSurfaceView glSurfaceView)
        throws SFBException
        Displays the remote participant's video. MMVRSurfaceView: MMVRSurface view is an implementation of the Android TextureView. It provides its own custom renderer. Clients are expected to create an instance of MMVRSurfaceView and add it to their layouts.
        Parameters:
        glSurfaceView - MMVRSurfaceView instance.
        Throws:
        SFBException - SFBException object.

      • canSubscribe

        Check if we can subscribe to participant video.
